{"tid":1166915,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"到底韓國有乜野吸引？歷史又係喺明朝到抄襲","createTime":"2019-05-22T17:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T18:32:48.000Z","uid":198503,"like":37,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2543f2ba1446d5aaebe88bf632888e6f41b0c35a","tid":1166915,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T17:34:15.000Z","msg":"真係on鳩鳩<br />\n<br />\n一街都係整容  <br />\n又無禮貌   講野粗聲粗氣<br />\n同鄰國農村一撚樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n古代個時做附屬國做左幾鳩百年<br />\n<br />\n去到唔知幾時朝鮮族先有機會出到位<br />\n打贏高句麗<br />\n<br />\n之後又要用晒中國啲野<br />\n<br />\n中文字  官服  龍袍  制度  地方名<br />\n<br />\n淨係識重蟲衝   寫埋啲字十足原始人學寫字咁<br />\n<br />\n睇韓劇基本上就係明朝加埋啲泡菜話<br />\n<br />\n是鳩但搬啲粗糧當上菜，泡菜，粗茶淡飯竟然係皇室食嘅菜餚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我諗唔到韓國到底有咩文化係值得啲人出晒水去一遊<br />\n<br />\n到而家都只係一班生蕃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nIgnorant country <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4185e5a0ae252963c117b77faee83bf294dd8c03","tid":1166915,"uid":194076,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T17:38:00.000Z","msg":"到底連登有乜野吸引？連登又係喺高登到抄襲"},{"pid":"65ade7eeccb136a50a6f64ef8efa2f45e43c7a08","tid":1166915,"uid":254259,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T17:58:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"532fc72650166836cdbb697028961aa408024cfc","tid":1166915,"uid":157407,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65ade7eeccb136a50a6f64ef8efa2f45e43c7a08","tid":1166915,"uid":254259,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T17:58:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T18:04:15.000Z","msg":"全世界都抄非洲 你都係想咁講啫"},{"pid":"0b16ab6e24b305589aac26c631a9e58bae190dbd","tid":1166915,"uid":254259,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T18:05:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e554cdd439f5e80e5d89b68943142a8c737edb9","tid":1166915,"uid":203797,"like":9,"dis